data.description: This beautiful 2-story, 3bedroom, 1 1/2 bathroom home was recently fully remodeled in 2020. Includes all new windows, new carpet, new driveway, basement was recently waterproofed in 2020 and partially finished in 2021. Also includes appliances in kitchen and brand new washer and dryer in basement. Great for an investment or residential property. Owner is a licensed real estate agent.
